item.title: Silverline Named to Deloitte's 2015 Technology Fast 500™
item.description:
Silverline Named to Deloitte's 2015 Technology Fast 500™

New York, NY - November 13, 2015 - Silverline today announced it ranked 304 on Deloitte's Technology Fast 500™, a ranking of the 500 fastest growing technology, media, telecommunications, life sciences and energy tech companies in North America. Silverline grew 220 percent during this period.
